# Motivation

- It is desired to be able to optionally monitor how long a task is active for a give system activity.

# Goals

- Allow developers to enable task profiling and later be able to implement hooks to collect collect active duration for each task.

# Release Impact: Minor

# Test Plan

- All regressin tests pass
